metadata.name: She's pop and cute.
metadata.description:
Pop-girls live colorfully today.
Her world is colorful and vivid everywhere. With her favorite doughnut in her hand, she lives freely today, expressing her own kawaii in her own way. She is not bound by anything.

ポップガールは今日もカラフルに生きている。
彼女の世界はどこまでもカラフルで鮮やか。大好きなドーナツを手に、今日も自分のkawaiiを自分自身で表現しながら自由に生きている。彼女は何にも囚われない。
